# Follow Existing Patterns

- Nothing in this project is new; default to existing patterns already used in nearby components/services.
- If asked to revisit the same issue more than once, assume pattern drift and compare against established implementations before changing code again.
- Prefer copying working structure from analogous files over inventing a new local pattern.
- Before changing behavior, inspect at least one mature component that solves the same problem (filtering, loading, mapping, shell coordination, etc.).
